summary:
Working in the international company with ambitious goals and constant strive for success.
Skincare is the expert in the protection of hands and we help people to pay more attention to Occupational Skin diseases by finding best solutions for each of them individually.
More than 1000 000 people rely on us in protection of their hands.
Is is not just about barrier creams or cleansing paste- is is about safety and health...
And health is one of the most precious things... because if we are healthy, we are happy.
